# No secrets are required for Milestones 1-2 (document download, local PDF
# parsing, and embedding are all local/pure HTTP operations).
#
# Milestone 3 (answer generation) requires a Groq API key — genuinely free,
# no billing/card required. Get one at https://console.groq.com/keys.
# Copy this file to .env (which is gitignored) and fill in your real key:
GROQ_API_KEY=
